[Episode 28]

24
00:01:34,150 --> 00:01:36,020
My Lord, did you drain your own power to refine

25
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,660
the Golden Millet Dream directly?

26
00:01:38,430 --> 00:01:39,850
Planting the Golden Millet Dream within someone

27
00:01:39,950 --> 00:01:41,180
takes an enormous amount of spiritual power,

28
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,620
and the process feels like being flayed alive.

29
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,690
You did all this so Ming Yi

30
00:01:45,950 --> 00:01:47,210
could take it directly,

31
00:01:47,230 --> 00:01:47,900
didn't you?

32
00:01:48,710 --> 00:01:50,130
Did you really go that far?

33
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,850
Sorry, Master.

34
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,380
I made an oath

35
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,740
and promised you

36
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,570
not to let Golden Millet Dream appear again,

37
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,380
but

38
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,010
I must save her.

39
00:03:35,430 --> 00:03:37,690
It's boring if you don't go crazy once.

40
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:39,340
I...

41
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:42,010
I really don't know what to say.

42
00:03:42,310 --> 00:03:44,170
You said you'd use the Golden Millet Dream as bait

43
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,380
to avenge Fairy Bo,

44
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,610
so you hadn't used it on yourself.

45
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,890
And now, you suddenly

46
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:49,130
offered it to someone.

47
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,890
You exhausted a lot of your spiritual power,

48
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,780
so you probably cannot use the Spirit Well anymore.

49
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,100
I'm worried that you'd suddenly do something rash

50
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,170
at the Qingyun Tournament,

51
00:03:56,310 --> 00:03:58,100
the Heavenly Grief in you relapse again suddenly,

52
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,570
but you can't even use the Spirit Well.

53
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:01,380
So you'll just die suddenly.

54
00:04:02,150 --> 00:04:04,130
If I had known, I shouldn't have listened to you

55
00:04:04,150 --> 00:04:05,980
and killed Ming Yi.

56
00:04:13,310 --> 00:04:14,100
All right.

57
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,730
It's my first time hearing you say so many things.

58
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:21,250
Drink a little.

59
00:04:22,310 --> 00:04:23,540
This is just temporary.

60
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,290
Spirit Well isn't gone.

61
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,220
I don't know what to say.

62
00:04:31,750 --> 00:04:32,290
I don't agree

63
00:04:32,310 --> 00:04:33,850
with you and Ming Yi being together.

64
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,900
Now that we have given her so much as the betrothal gift,

65
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:37,540
you must marry her no matter what!

66
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,250
Well said!

67
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,490
Do you think I was serious?

68
00:04:39,510 --> 00:04:40,140
Of course.

69
00:04:40,270 --> 00:04:40,850
I...

70
00:04:44,270 --> 00:04:45,580
I'm sure she knows everything now.

71
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,930
I hope she is sensible

72
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,730
and will marry you immediately to repay you.

73
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,020
Buxiu,

74
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,250
no one offers a medicine

75
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:53,850
and expects the other person to marry him in return.

76
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:54,980
Besides,

77
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,170
why must she repay me?

78
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,980
Did you not even tell her that?

79
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,140
I...

80
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,370
You are not giving her an ordinary medicine.

81
00:05:04,390 --> 00:05:05,660
You are giving her your life!

82
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:10,660
Indeed, she doesn't know it was me who saved her.

83
00:05:10,830 --> 00:05:11,780
She thought

84
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:13,100
it was Situ Ling

85
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,290
who exchanged his heart's blood

86
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,660
for her lifespan.

87
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,340
What in the world?

88
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,610
I don't know what to say.

89
00:05:20,870 --> 00:05:22,140
Heart's blood

90
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,610
can only extend one's lifespan for a few hours.

91
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:24,610
Did she think

92
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:26,020
