93
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,660
My Lord, Ming Yi isn't a fool.

94
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,810
Why would she believe that?

95
00:05:31,510 --> 00:05:33,340
Situ Ling must have acted like a magnanimous savior too.

96
00:05:34,310 --> 00:05:35,340
Oh, that was my heart's blood.

97
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,900
I stabbed myself for you.

98
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:37,900
Ming Yi was charmed.

99
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,930
And so touched she was that...

100
00:05:45,830 --> 00:05:46,980
My Lord, have you told Ming Yi

101
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,540
