102
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:49,810
Not yet.

103
00:05:51,190 --> 00:05:51,900
I understand.

104
00:05:53,070 --> 00:05:54,250
I'll go and kill Situ Ling now.

105
00:05:54,270 --> 00:05:55,250
What do you understand?

106
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,250
Come back.

107
00:05:58,390 --> 00:05:59,540
You're not going to tell Ming Yi

108
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,660
Situ Ling's true identity

109
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,100
