110
00:06:02,510 --> 00:06:03,370
Now, you're letting Ming Yi

111
00:06:03,390 --> 00:06:04,700
think it was Situ Ling who saved her.

112
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,900
How can you marry her if you do that?

113
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,100
Ming Yi isn't that kind of person.

114
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,540
She won't marry someone

115
00:06:11,830 --> 00:06:12,900
because they saved her.

116
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,340
It's pointless.

117
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:16,850
I want her

118
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,170
to marry me willingly.

119
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,340
I forgot to tell you.

120
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,700
I moved to Shouhua Academy as well

121
00:06:52,750 --> 00:06:53,980
to make training more convenient.

122
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:55,020
I'm staying downstairs.

