00:08:09,190 --> 00:08:09,930
Immortal Ji.

144
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:50,010
We meet again, old friend.

145
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,130
Immortal Situ.

146
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,340
Ming Yi.

147
00:09:10,510 --> 00:09:11,490
Can I go in?

148
00:09:12,870 --> 00:09:13,580
Please come in.

149
00:09:18,270 --> 00:09:19,180
Why are you here?

150
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,850
I heard Fairy Zhang Tai say

151
00:09:28,150 --> 00:09:29,300
you've moved to Shouhua Academy.

152
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,700
Ming Yi, have you recovered?

153
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,370
Yes.

154
00:09:36,150 --> 00:09:38,010
It's all thanks to you, Immortal Situ.

155
00:09:38,510 --> 00:09:39,580
You've helped me so much.

156
00:09:39,670 --> 00:09:41,770
I don't know what I can do to repay you.

157
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:42,340
Tell me...

158
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:42,940
Ming Yi.

159
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:45,220
Your identity will be exposed easily here.

160
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,580
You must leave with me.

161
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,130
I can't leave.

162
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:51,180
Why?

163
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,250
I promised the Empress

164
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:55,010
to help her out at Shouhua Academy.

165
00:09:55,270 --> 00:09:56,490
Besides, the tea gathering will happen soon.

166
00:09:56,510 --> 00:09:57,610
I can't leave.

167
00:09:57,630 --> 00:09:58,370
Ming Yi.

168
00:09:59,120 --> 00:09:59,730
Ming Yi.

169
00:10:00,030 --> 00:10:01,130
You said you were cold last night.

170
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,940
I prepared a blanket specially for you.

171
00:10:05,510 --> 00:10:06,730
Immortal Situ, you're here too?

172
00:10:06,910 --> 00:10:08,370
You didn't even tell me we have a guest.

173
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:09,890
Forgive me for not welcoming you.

174
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:16,820
Since he's already here,

175
00:10:17,270 --> 00:10:18,530
let's invite him to have a meal together.

176
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:20,180
Ming Yi,

177
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,370
why is he here?

178
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:25,610
He is here...

179
00:10:25,790 --> 00:10:27,610
Of course, I'm here to accompany my wife.

180
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,490
What's wrong?

181
00:10:28,510 --> 00:10:29,250
Ji Bozai.

182
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,010
I'm sure you haven't eaten yet, Ming Yi.

183
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,730
The teahouse has a few new dishes.

184
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,340
Let me treat you to a meal.

185
00:10:43,670 --> 00:10:45,010
How can we let you treat us?

186
00:10:45,030 --> 00:10:46,700
You are our guest, Immortal Situ.

187
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,980
I should be the one treating you.

188
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:56,980
What do you say, Ming Yi?

189
00:10:59,200 --> 00:10:59,890
I...

190
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:04,940
I want...

191
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,580
I want

192
00:11:07,150 --> 00:11:08,300
both of you to eat without me.

193
00:11:17,390 --> 00:11:18,130
Are you not coming?

194
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,650
Fresh flowers!

195
00:11:44,870 --> 00:11:46,300
Have a look at some fresh flowers, miss!

196
00:11:49,030 --> 00:11:50,180
Have a look at the flowers.

197
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,580
Lanterns!

198
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,010
What a coincidence.

199
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,340
Did you come here to eat, too?

200
00:12:03,030 --> 00:12:03,730
Let's eat together.

201
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:15,940
The new dishes taste better than the old ones.

202
00:12:16,550 --> 00:12:17,340
Try them, Ming Yi.

203
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:31,650
Only two people can sit here.

204
00:12:35,630 --> 00:12:36,770
Why are you still here then?

205
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:38,100
Don't you think you're a nuisance?

206
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:46,100
Here.

207
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,300
This is your favorite.

208
00:12:49,030 --> 00:12:50,220
You should try this instead.

209
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:54,420
Something that you haven't tried before is always better.

210
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,250
Let me try it.

211
00:13:09,870 --> 00:13:10,730
It tastes so bad.

212
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:30,770
It's rancid.

213
00:13:42,790 --> 00:13:43,370
Fine.

214
00:13:43,630 --> 00:13:45,530
Enjoy the food. Don't waste anything.

215
00:13:45,550 --> 00:13:46,250
I'll be leaving.

216
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:48,180
They will pay for me.

217
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:49,370
Sure.

218
00:13:53,910 --> 00:13:55,530
Immortal Situ, thanks for paying the bill.

219
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:57,580
However, I must remind you

220
00:13:58,510 --> 00:14:00,490
that you know who you truly are.

221
00:14:05,030 --> 00:14:07,650
If you insist on approaching my wife, Ming Yi,

222
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,530
and bring trouble to her,

223
00:14:10,270 --> 00:14:11,820
I won't forgive you.

224
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:13,820
What do you mean?

225
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:25,130
Sir, pack them for me.

226
00:14:25,550 --> 00:14:26,100
Sure.

227
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:40,850
Buy two, get one free!

228
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,820
Final two pairs!

229
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:44,420
Thank you.

230
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:45,250
Take care.

231
00:14:50,630 --> 00:14:51,250
Sorry.

232
00:14:52,750 --> 00:14:53,490
Watch where you're going!

233
00:14:57,510 --> 00:14:58,420
Fresh flowers!

234
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:00,820
Take a look at some fresh flowers!

235
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:08,490
Excuse me.

236
00:15:10,180 --> 00:15:14,060
ظآزMaybe I'm just your fireflyظآز

237
00:15:16,700 --> 00:15:20,660
ظآزThat's why I'm so fragileظآز

238
00:15:21,780 --> 00:15:24,900
ظآزIn this world, there's too muchظآز

239
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:28,180
ظآزCause and effect of love and hate surgingظآز

240
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:33,980
ظآزWould you be willing to stay for me?ظآز

241
00:15:37,060 --> 00:15:42,620
ظآزIf your night is cold, with no warmth of the sunظآز

242
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:49,060
ظآزPut my burning heart in your chestظآز

243
00:15:49,780 --> 00:15:54,220
ظآزEven in this restless worldظآز

244
00:15:54,260 --> 00:15:57,420
ظآزMy faint lightظآز

245
00:15:57,540 --> 00:16:02,300
ظآزWill shine through for your brillianceظآز

246
00:16:02,700 --> 00:16:08,300
ظآزIf your world was once an endless wastelandظآز

247
00:16:09,100 --> 00:16:14,740
ظآزI'd tear myself apart to fill the wounds inside youظآز

248
00:16:15,460 --> 00:16:19,900
ظآزEven if this life is like a shooting starظآز

249
00:16:19,900 --> 00:16:23,140
ظآزBrief only for the sake of meeting youظآز

250
00:16:23,180 --> 00:16:28,020
ظآزIn this fleeting life, I'll still be your lightظآز

251
00:16:53,550 --> 00:16:54,340
Fuyue.

252
00:16:56,750 --> 00:16:58,220
No matter how much I've done

253
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:01,580
and how long I've waited,

254
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:08,180
when I see her eyes again,

255
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,530
they

256
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:15,010
are still the same as before.

257
00:17:17,270 --> 00:17:18,490
She does not see me.

258
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:29,330
My Lord,

259
00:17:30,550 --> 00:17:32,570
I will never betray you.

260
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:34,330
If you want,

261
00:17:34,830 --> 00:17:36,730
I can share my lifespan with you.

262
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:40,530
Is it worth it?

263
00:17:44,750 --> 00:17:48,860
You did so much for Ming Yi, but it was all in vain.

264
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:52,570
Have you asked yourself the same question as well?

265
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:56,700
I thought it was worth it in the beginning.

266
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:02,940
But I asked myself again and again today,

267
00:18:07,510 --> 00:18:09,090
what can I do for her

268
00:18:12,110 --> 00:18:13,620
that I haven't done yet?

269
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:17,700
