00:36:23,280 --> 00:36:25,170
Twenty-Seven is quite smart.

552
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:27,570
Did he just so happen

553
00:36:27,590 --> 00:36:28,570
to steal this

554
00:36:28,590 --> 00:36:30,420
from Ming Xin?

555
00:36:30,440 --> 00:36:31,130
Who knows?

556
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:33,260
Perhaps it's because you are the owner.

557
00:36:33,440 --> 00:36:34,380
The cat is just like its owner.

558
00:36:38,150 --> 00:36:39,780
Although we are still missing one piece,

559
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:41,690
it's enough to see some things.

560
00:36:49,280 --> 00:36:50,610
The Heavenly Grief you asked for.

561
00:36:52,030 --> 00:36:53,090
Thank you, Lord Hanfeng.

562
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:56,130
With the Heavenly Grief,

563
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:57,530
Ming Xian

564
00:36:58,150 --> 00:37:00,780
will no longer be the Warrior God of Yaoguang Mountain.

565
00:37:05,630 --> 00:37:07,860
It was Ming Xin who made the deal with Mu Qibai.

566
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:09,740
I can recognize his voice even if he is mute,

567
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:11,690
let alone not seeing his face.

568
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:14,900
Twenty-Seven is an amazing thief.

569
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:16,090
He stole this.

570
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:19,300
Are you missing something?

571
00:37:21,190 --> 00:37:22,260
It seems like Ming Xin

572
00:37:23,110 --> 00:37:24,900
was the one who poisoned you with Heavenly Grief.

573
00:37:28,190 --> 00:37:30,010
The truth is not surprising at all.

574
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:33,690
The missing piece of the Recording Mirror

575
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,130
is probably with Ming Xin.

576
00:37:35,670 --> 00:37:37,820
I must get it during the tea gathering this time

577
00:37:37,840 --> 00:37:39,460
so that I have complete evidence

578
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:41,090
to prove that it was Ming Xin who poisoned me.

579
00:37:43,070 --> 00:37:45,610
Oh, one more thing.

580
00:37:46,670 --> 00:37:48,650
You were grateful to Situ Ling for saving you

581
00:37:49,400 --> 00:37:50,610
and didn't expose his identity.

582
00:37:51,800 --> 00:37:53,010
I asked Buxiu to find out who he is.

583
00:37:54,760 --> 00:37:55,980
You know everything now?

584
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:57,980
Yes.

585
00:37:58,670 --> 00:37:59,780
I also found out

586
00:38:00,480 --> 00:38:02,570
Situ Ling is the youngest son of Zhushui's Emperor,

587
00:38:03,630 --> 00:38:04,380
Chao Yuan.

588
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:07,650
He came to Jixing Abyss for the Golden Millet Dream.

589
00:38:10,960 --> 00:38:13,940
He saved me after I came out of Wugui Sea.

590
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:16,820
He told me honestly that he was from Zhushui Spiritual State

591
00:38:17,230 --> 00:38:19,690
and that he came to Jixing Abyss for the Golden Millet Dream.

592
00:38:20,480 --> 00:38:21,460
Moreover...

593
00:38:21,510 --> 00:38:22,340
Are you all right?

594
00:38:23,320 --> 00:38:24,490
We must leave here immediately.

595
00:38:24,710 --> 00:38:25,980
Zhushui Spiritual State has a backup plan.

596
00:38:28,280 --> 00:38:29,010
How do you know that?

597
00:38:32,110 --> 00:38:33,780
No wonder he went to the Sunken Abyss that day

598
00:38:34,030 --> 00:38:35,170
without waiting for us.

599
00:38:35,920 --> 00:38:38,380
He even gave Master She the Bo's Medical Classics he found.

600
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:40,530
That was when Master and I started feeling suspicious.

601
00:38:42,190 --> 00:38:43,090
In that case,

602
00:38:43,110 --> 00:38:44,170
he is still a dangerous person.

603
00:38:52,400 --> 00:38:53,130
You're back.

604
00:38:53,590 --> 00:38:54,340
Father.

605
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:57,530
I've found the complete formula for the Golden Millet Dream

606
00:38:58,030 --> 00:38:59,170
and all the herbs required.

607
00:39:00,070 --> 00:39:01,940
However, the catalyst herb, Diwu tree's core,

608
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:04,050
has been extinct for 10,000 years.

609
00:39:04,590 --> 00:39:06,740
I don't know where to find it.

610
00:39:08,190 --> 00:39:09,820
Please aid me, Father.

611
00:39:11,550 --> 00:39:13,530
Do you think I will have something

612
00:39:14,280 --> 00:39:16,010
that has been extinct for 10,000 years?

613
00:39:17,510 --> 00:39:19,300
If it cannot be found in Zhushui Spiritual State,

614
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:21,460
then there's no need

615
00:39:21,460 --> 00:39:21,940
[Bo's Medical Classics]

616
00:39:22,510 --> 00:39:24,460
for this formula to remain in this world.

617
00:39:35,150 --> 00:39:36,170
Father,

618
00:39:36,710 --> 00:39:39,300
I'm the only one who has read the whole book.

619
00:39:40,590 --> 00:39:41,650
I remember

620
00:39:42,510 --> 00:39:44,050
every word in it

621
00:39:44,280 --> 00:39:46,460
and can copy it down any time.

622
00:39:47,320 --> 00:39:49,090
Once I make this medicine,

623
00:39:49,630 --> 00:39:51,820
I'll surely hand it over to you, Father.

624
00:40:08,070 --> 00:40:08,860
Chao Yuan,

625
00:40:09,880 --> 00:40:12,980
you've achieved this mastery with the Thousand Insect Spell.

626
00:40:13,880 --> 00:40:14,980
You are also braver

627
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:16,740
than you were in the past.

628
00:40:17,710 --> 00:40:20,260
You actually dare negotiate with me.

629
00:40:20,630 --> 00:40:21,610
Great.

630
00:40:22,230 --> 00:40:24,050
I like it a lot.

631
00:40:27,190 --> 00:40:29,300
You've laid low for many years.

632
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:31,090
Tell me

633
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:33,130
what your ambition is.

634
00:40:37,110 --> 00:40:38,650
I want to grow my own spiritual veins

635
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:40,820
and become the ruler of Zhushui Spiritual State

636
00:40:40,840 --> 00:40:42,570
that everyone admires.

637
00:40:43,630 --> 00:40:46,090
I want to become the heir whom you recognize.

638
00:40:48,440 --> 00:40:50,650
I want you to tell me everything.

639
00:40:51,400 --> 00:40:52,900
Under your arrangement,

640
00:40:54,030 --> 00:40:56,570
what will become of Zhushui Spiritual State

641
00:40:57,110 --> 00:40:58,980
and the Qingyun Tournament?

642
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:05,900
I want

643
00:41:07,440 --> 00:41:08,820
to overcome destiny itself.

644
00:41:16,190 --> 00:41:17,650
Among my sons,

645
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:19,690
you resemble me the most.

646
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:26,130
Two years ago, Jixing Abyss lost in the tournament

647
00:41:26,630 --> 00:41:30,050
and had to offer a tribute to Yaoguang Mountain and our realm.

648
00:41:30,710 --> 00:41:32,260
The rarest of the tributes

649
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:35,530
were two wilted roots of Diwu tree.

650
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:38,300
The one offered to Yaoguang Mountain

651
00:41:38,400 --> 00:41:39,740
was stolen by Bo Yulan.

652
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:40,610
That was why

653
00:41:41,070 --> 00:41:43,690
Bo Yulan was caught by Mu Qibai.

654
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:45,980
The remaining one

655
00:41:46,760 --> 00:41:48,340
was sent to this realm.

656
00:41:52,190 --> 00:41:53,690
It's up to you now

657
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:55,530
to nurture it back to health.

658
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,260
Thank you, Father.

659
